    "17 This detailed approach, however, is rather the exception.",
    "According to the compilation on 6 May 2023 by Solis (2023), among the 100 largest German universities, 2% applied a general prohibition on the use of ChatGPT, 23% granted partial permission, 12% generally permitted its use, while 63% of the universities had none or only vague guidelines in this respect.",
